TITLE: Typegoose Enhanced Model Definition
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the simplified Typegoose approach using decorators to define Mongoose models with TypeScript classes, showing various property types and relationships.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typegoose/typegoose/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
class Job {
