TITLE: Using AutoIncrementID from @typegoose/auto-increment
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to use the AutoIncrementID plugin from @typegoose/auto-increment, which increments the _id field for new documents.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typegoose/typegoose/blob/master/docs/guides/integration-examples/common-plugins.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_10

