TITLE: Using addNullToEnum Option in Typegoose
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the use of addNullToEnum option to add null to the enum array. This doesn't work if the value is required.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typegoose/typegoose/blob/master/docs/api/decorators/prop.md#2025-04-17_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
